{"tid":1148702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位港豬, 強国好快搵香港出氣同開刀補血","createTime":"2019-05-10T15:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T15:46:38.000Z","uid":76310,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7718f132c42e43ee71fa9ca29e7e96ea3af7ebde","tid":1148702,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T15:33:27.000Z","msg":"各位港豬, 強国好快搵香港出氣同開刀補血<br />\n企穩啦<br />\n<br />\n豬瘟, 害蟲, 關稅, 強国比人扣左好多血<br />\n加速通過逃犯條例, 搵港豬補血<br />\n抄在香港強国貪官, 抄港資, 抄地產霸權, 抄大商家, 抄有錢人, 抄中產, 抄外資, 抄外匯儲備, 抄財政儲備, 抄mpf, 抄存款<br />\n這樣才能為強国補血<br />\n<br />\n各位睇路了<br />\n支爆前必先港爆<br />\n支爆前找替死鬼去捱去擋, 當然香港人的身家財產就是護身符和替死鬼<br />\n<br />\n有心理準備, 當強国天災不斷發生, 比國際包圍, 比美帝包圍<br />\n香港, 港豬, 要不斷被放血開刀"},{"pid":"367064e0b0cd6fa2c419b262e8c713b33cf891ce","tid":1148702,"uid":41389,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T15:34:39.000Z","msg":"爆囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想見到有錢人再唔做奶共狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c758bd81bc8677b7525159c42864a477712ab2","tid":1148702,"uid":63940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T15:39:56.000Z","msg":"小市民唔洗驚住，佢一過再慢慢諗點攞走啲錢喇，反而驚外資撒資失業率上升<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後就&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"1e4d3cd8c5d1cdfa5cf044836c5636da79f45b09","tid":1148702,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15c758bd81bc8677b7525159c42864a477712ab2","tid":1148702,"uid":63940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T15:39:56.000Z","msg":"小市民唔洗驚住，佢一過再慢慢諗點攞走啲錢喇，反而驚外資撒資失業率上升<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後就&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T15:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.g